title: Video Game Graphics Have Become Too Real...
description:
Hello guys and gals, it's me Mutahar again! This time we take a look at what appears to be a new game known as "Unrecord" which seems to be creating a new bodycam style FPS game that has quite possibly the most photorealistic visuals I've seen. This also provides a good opportunity to look into some of the newest rendering tech that exists today. Thanks for watching!
Like, Comment and Subscribe for more videos!
